# Dual 32 GB GPU model set — 2× RTX 6000 Ada / A6000 / similar (64 GB total, tp=2)
# Format: <short-name>  [<gguf-file>]  [<params>]  [hf:<tokenizer-repo>]
#
# vs. 2x24gb.vllm (48 GB):
#   +16 GiB total → ~double KV headroom for 70B models
#   llama3.3:70b: max_model_len 32768 (48 GB) → 65536 (64 GB)
#   72B/70B models can now run at higher quant (Q5_K_M) or higher context
#   gpt-oss:120b (MXFP4 ~60 GiB): first config where 120B is fully GPU-resident
#
# GGUFs not in default.vllm — download before first use:
#   ./fetch-hf.sh models/2x32gb.vllm
#   (fetch-hf.sh uses hf: fields to locate GGUF files on HuggingFace Hub)
#
# Run with:
#   ./run.sh --backend vllm --model-file models/2x32gb.vllm --models llama3.3:70b-q5km
#   ./compare.sh --backend vllm --model-file models/2x32gb.vllm

# ── llama3.3:70b — more context vs. 2x24gb.vllm ──────────────────────────────
# Q4_K_S (~37 GiB): proven at max_model_len=32768 on 48 GB; extra 16 GiB → 65536 feasible.
# Tokenizer is gated (meta-llama) — set HF_TOKEN or populate hf-token.txt.
llama3.3:70b-q4ks  Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-Q4_K_S.gguf  tp=2,dtype=auto,max_model_len=65536  hf:meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct

# Q5_K_M (~48 GiB): higher quality; leaves ~8 GiB KV total → max_model_len=32768.
# New GGUF — not in default.vllm; run ./fetch-hf.sh models/2x32gb.vllm first.
# Tokenizer same gated repo as Q4_K_S above.
llama3.3:70b-q5km  Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-Q5_K_M.gguf  tp=2,dtype=auto,max_model_len=32768  hf:meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct

# ── qwen2.5-coder:72b — coding-focused 72B; new GGUF ─────────────────────────
# Q4_K_M (~40 GiB): ~12 GiB/GPU for weights → ~16 GiB KV total → max_model_len=32768.
# (64 GB × 0.9 − 40 GiB = 17.6 GiB KV; 65536 × 320 KB/token = 21 GiB → exceeds budget;
#  use max_model_len=32768 which needs only ~10.5 GiB KV.)
# New GGUF — run ./fetch-hf.sh models/2x32gb.vllm to download.
qwen2.5-coder:72b  Qwen2.5-Coder-72B-Instruct-Q4_K_M.gguf  tp=2,dtype=auto,max_model_len=32768  hf:Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-72B-Instruct

# ── deepseek-r1:70b — thinking; Llama-70B distill ────────────────────────────
# Q4_K_M (~37 GiB): same weight footprint as llama3.3:70b Q4_K_S → ~16 GiB KV.
# New GGUF — run ./fetch-hf.sh models/2x32gb.vllm to download.
deepseek-r1:70b  DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Llama-70B-Q4_K_M.gguf  tp=2,dtype=auto,max_model_len=32768,thinking  hf:deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Llama-70B
